Package: CharityNavigatoR
Type: Package
Title: Charity Navigator API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person('Jose Andres', 'Montes Lopez', email = 'jam2448@columbia.edu', role = c('aut','cre'))
Description: Founded in 2001, Charity Navigator has become the nation's largest and most-utilized evaluator of charities.
        The company provides charity data and a proprietery rating system through a REST API.
        The CharityClient package provides an family of R functions that access the API service, making it accessible
        and R-friendly for R researchers.
        See https://charity.3scale.net/docs/data-api/reference#api-documentation for the Charity Navigator API schema.
